with the record.

439
00:23:42,733 --> 00:23:44,367
I'll take care of this,
Enriquez.

440
00:23:52,367 --> 00:23:53,133
Enriquez,

441
00:23:53,533 --> 00:23:55,000
let's meet at the station, okay?

442
00:23:56,100 --> 00:23:57,367
Why, Sir? Where are you going?

443
00:23:59,333 --> 00:24:01,067
I have something important
to take care of.

444
00:24:04,233 --> 00:24:05,167
What about the sketch?

445
00:24:06,600 --> 00:24:07,667
I'll take care of it.

446
00:24:08,267 --> 00:24:10,100
Here, you can take the car.

447
00:24:14,333 --> 00:24:15,000
Okay, Sir.

448
00:24:38,600 --> 00:24:39,900
Can I talk to you?

449
00:24:40,633 --> 00:24:42,467
Tonyo, is there a problem?

450
00:24:43,100 --> 00:24:44,467
Just make sure

451
00:24:44,800 --> 00:24:47,133
that all your answers
to my questions are true.

452
00:24:48,200 --> 00:24:49,767
If not, we'll end up fighting.

453
00:24:49,900 --> 00:24:51,433
Is this about Daga?

454
00:24:51,867 --> 00:24:54,967
You know, son, they're just
trying to ruin my name.

455
00:24:55,433 --> 00:24:56,800
It's not about him.

456
00:24:57,467 --> 00:25:01,733
It's About the museum robbery
and the San Isidro bank robbery.

457
00:25:03,833 --> 00:25:05,067
Did you have anything
to do with that?

458
00:25:07,067 --> 00:25:09,367
I'll have my fingers cut off

459
00:25:10,000 --> 00:25:12,600
if you discover that I had
anything to do with it.

460
00:25:34,367 --> 00:25:36,933
The gun is registered to
Victor Santiago,

461
00:25:37,100 --> 00:25:38,967
but is that enough evidence
to prove

462
00:25:39,100 --> 00:25:40,267
that he really shot Bullet?

463
00:25:40,400 --> 00:25:41,700
Well, that was 10 years ago.

464
00:25:41,833 --> 00:25:43,033
Well, if it wasn't him,

465
00:25:43,167 --> 00:25:45,133
then this is a terrible
coincidence.

466
00:25:45,267 --> 00:25:47,700
Let's start with the mask used
in the bank,

467
00:25:47,833 --> 00:25:51,967
then the poison used on Sonny,
and the bullet in Bullet's head.

468
00:25:52,100 --> 00:25:52,900
Come on, come with me.

469
00:25:53,033 --> 00:25:53,600
Where, Sir?

470
00:25:53,733 --> 00:25:54,967
Daga was killed.

471
00:25:55,100 --> 00:25:57,100
Do you have any idea who did it?

472
00:25:57,233 --> 00:25:58,333
No name was mentioned,

473
00:25:58,467 --> 00:26:01,267
but I heard it from Daga's own
mouth that he was talking

474
00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:03,367
to a policeman,

475
00:26:03,500 --> 00:26:05,567
a policeman he trusted.

476
00:26:05,700 --> 00:26:06,233
Tonyo?
